\details{
The literature search queried Web of Science Core Collection on 2023-08-21
using biologging-related terms. Results were limited to twelve subject
categories (e.g. Ecology, Zoology, Marine & Freshwater Biology) with 100+
papers each. Each paper was scored by at least two reviewers in two passes:
a broad pass (columns documented here) and a fine-scale pass (work in
progress at time of release). See the project methods page for full details:
\url{https://flukeandfeather.github.io/openbiologging/methods.html}

Sensor categories follow Williams et al. (2019):
\doi{10.1111/1365-2656.13094}
}
